{"id": "anc_drawer", "modality": "animations", "name": "Drawer", "task": {"description": "Create a self-contained 1920x1080 HTML animation (inline CSS, NO <canvas>) of a side drawer. A content page (a header bar plus a few aligned rows) is visible; over ~2.5s a 380px-wide drawer panel slides in from the RIGHT edge and a dim overlay fades over the rest of the page. The drawer contains a title and 4 aligned menu rows. The drawer settles flush against the right edge.", "requirements": ["The drawer panel stays fully within the viewport at every frame (it settles flush to the right edge, not past it)", "The drawer visibly slides in over time (its x-position moves leftward into view across frames)", "By the final frame the drawer is fully open and its 4 menu rows are visible and left-aligned", "The drawer does not overlap or clip its own menu rows (text stays inside the panel)", "The underlying page content is not pushed off-screen (the drawer overlays, it does not displace content off the viewport)", "No horizontal scrollbar appears at any frame"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 9, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2456, "rv_n_defects": 1, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 11583}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 17, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2673, "rv_n_defects": 2, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 11836}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 19, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2650, "rv_n_defects": 5, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 12252}], "ss_img": "images/animations/anc_drawer_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/animations/anc_drawer_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Side Drawer Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        /* Main Content */\n        .main-content {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .header-bar {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 80px;\n            background: #2c3e50;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 0 40px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .header-title {\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 28px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n        }\n\n        .content-rows {\n            padding: 60px 80px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .content-row {\n            background: white;\n            padding: 32px 40px;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;\n        }\n\n        .row-title {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 12px;\n        }\n\n        .row-content {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: #7f8c8d;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        /* Overlay */\n        .overlay {\n            position: fixed;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n            z-index: 2;\n            opacity: 0;\n            animation: fadeInOverlay 2.5s ease-out forwards;\n            animation-delay: 0.2s;\n        }\n\n        /* Side Drawer */\n        .side-drawer {\n            position: fixed;\n            top: 0;\n            right: -380px;\n            width: 380px;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: white;\n            z-index: 3;\n            box-shadow: -4px 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n            animation: slideInDrawer 2.5s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94) forwards;\n        }\n\n        .drawer-header {\n            height: 80px;\n            background: #34495e;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 0 32px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #ecf0f1;\n        }\n\n        .drawer-title {\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 22px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            letter-spacing: 0.3px;\n        }\n\n        .drawer-content {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 20px 32px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #ecf0f1;\n            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item:hover {\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        .menu-icon {\n            width: 24px;\n            height: 24px;\n            background: #3498db;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            margin-right: 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            flex-shrink: 0;\n        }\n\n        .menu-icon::after {\n            content: '';\n            width: 8px;\n            height: 8px;\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n        }\n\n        .menu-text {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            font-weight: 500;\n        }\n\n        /* Animations */\n        @keyframes slideInDrawer {\n            0% {\n                right: -380px;\n            }\n            100% {\n                right: 0;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeInOverlay {\n            0% {\n                opacity: 0;\n            }\n            100% {\n                opacity: 1;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- Main Content -->\n    <div class=\"main-content\">\n        <div class=\"header-bar\">\n            <div class=\"header-title\">Dashboard Overview</div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"content-rows\">\n            <div class=\"content-row\">\n                <div class=\"row-title\">Analytics Summary</div>\n                <div class=\"row-content\">View comprehensive analytics and performance metrics for your application with real-time data visualization and insights.</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-row\">\n                <div class=\"row-title\">User Management</div>\n                <div class=\"row-content\">Manage user accounts, permissions, and access controls with advanced filtering and bulk operations capabilities.</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-row\">\n                <div class=\"row-title\">System Configuration</div>\n                <div class=\"row-content\">Configure system settings, integrations, and preferences to optimize your workflow and operational efficiency.</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-row\">\n                <div class=\"row-title\">Reports & Export</div>\n                <div class=\"row-content\">Generate detailed reports and export data in multiple formats for analysis and compliance requirements.</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Overlay -->\n    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n\n    <!-- Side Drawer -->\n    <div class=\"side-drawer\">\n        <div class=\"drawer-header\">\n            <div class=\"drawer-title\">Navigation Menu</div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"drawer-content\">\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <div class=\"menu-icon\"></div>\n                <div class=\"menu-text\">Dashboard</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <div class=\"menu-icon\"></div>\n                <div class=\"menu-text\">Analytics</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <div class=\"menu-icon\"></div>\n                <div class=\"menu-text\">Settings</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <div class=\"menu-icon\"></div>\n                <div class=\"menu-text\">Profile</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Side Drawer Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        /* Main Content */\n        .main-content {\n            width: 1540px;\n            height: 100%;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .header-bar {\n            background: #2c3e50;\n            color: white;\n            height: 80px;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 0 40px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .header-title {\n            font-size: 28px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            letter-spacing: -0.5px;\n        }\n\n        .content-rows {\n            padding: 40px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 24px;\n        }\n\n        .content-row {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            padding: 32px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;\n            max-width: 1460px;\n        }\n\n        .row-title {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 12px;\n        }\n\n        .row-content {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: #5a6c7d;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        /* Overlay */\n        .overlay {\n            position: fixed;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 1540px;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n            z-index: 2;\n            opacity: 0;\n            animation: fadeInOverlay 2.5s ease-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        /* Side Drawer */\n        .side-drawer {\n            position: fixed;\n            top: 0;\n            right: -380px;\n            width: 380px;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: white;\n            box-shadow: -4px 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n            z-index: 3;\n            animation: slideInDrawer 2.5s ease-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        .drawer-header {\n            background: #34495e;\n            color: white;\n            height: 80px;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 0 32px;\n        }\n\n        .drawer-title {\n            font-size: 20px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            letter-spacing: -0.3px;\n        }\n\n        .drawer-menu {\n            padding: 32px 0;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 20px 32px;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #ecf0f1;\n            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item:hover {\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item:last-child {\n            border-bottom: none;\n        }\n\n        .menu-icon {\n            width: 24px;\n            height: 24px;\n            margin-right: 16px;\n            background: #3498db;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n        }\n\n        /* Animations */\n        @keyframes fadeInOverlay {\n            0% {\n                opacity: 0;\n            }\n            100% {\n                opacity: 1;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes slideInDrawer {\n            0% {\n                right: -380px;\n            }\n            100% {\n                right: 0;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- Main Content -->\n    <div class=\"main-content\">\n        <div class=\"header-bar\">\n            <div class=\"header-title\">Dashboard Overview</div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"content-rows\">\n            <div class=\"content-row\">\n                <div class=\"row-title\">Analytics Summary</div>\n                <div class=\"row-content\">Track your key performance indicators and monitor business growth with real-time data visualization and comprehensive reporting tools.</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-row\">\n                <div class=\"row-title\">User Management</div>\n                <div class=\"row-content\">Manage user accounts, permissions, and access controls across your organization with advanced security features and role-based authentication.</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-row\">\n                <div class=\"row-title\">Project Timeline</div>\n                <div class=\"row-content\">View project milestones, deadlines, and team assignments in an intuitive timeline interface that keeps everyone aligned and productive.</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-row\">\n                <div class=\"row-title\">System Settings</div>\n                <div class=\"row-content\">Configure application preferences, notification settings, and integration options to customize your workflow and optimize performance.</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Overlay -->\n    <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n\n    <!-- Side Drawer -->\n    <div class=\"side-drawer\">\n        <div class=\"drawer-header\">\n            <div class=\"drawer-title\">Navigation Menu</div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"drawer-menu\">\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <div class=\"menu-icon\">\ud83d\udcca</div>\n                <div>Analytics</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <div class=\"menu-icon\">\ud83d\udc65</div>\n                <div>Users</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <div class=\"menu-icon\">\ud83d\udccb</div>\n                <div>Projects</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <div class=\"menu-icon\">\u2699\ufe0f</div>\n                <div>Settings</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}